commit_message:
Basic compatibility for Windows

 * Don't name scripts foo.cmd, as that aliases to foo, and by default runs as a cmd bat file, which this definitely is not.
 * Don't import pwd at the top level, as that's not available on non-unix environments. Luckily you don't need it in Windows either

author: Christian Gati
commit_message:
Remove use of deprecated getchildren method

As of python 3.9, the method "getchildren" has been removed from the
xml.etree.ElementTree.Element object.[0] As this method has been deprecated
since python 3.2 and cloudtoken's minimum required python version is
3.5, this change switches to iteration on the Element object.

[0] https://docs.python.org/3.8/library/xml.etree.elementtree.html#xml.etree.ElementTree.Element.getchildren
